Title: Energy-Momentum Tensor Improvements in Two Dimensions
Authors: S. Deser and R. Jackiw
Comments: 11 pages in REVTeX
Report-no: MIT-CTP-2469
\\
  We discuss some aspects of the two-dimensional scalar field, considering
particularly the action for the conformal anomaly as an ``improved''
gravitational coupling, and the possibility of introducing a dual coupling,
which provides a ``chiral'' energy-momentum tensor improvement.
